channel.description:
OK so I'm trying to make a new server off of Elite-pk. I do not have any picture atm because i haven't really done any coding because i completely FAIL at it. after a lot of coding and such i think that this server will be pretty success full and it will most likely be on for a very long time.
Ill be adding a New Staff zone, donater Island and customs just for them. Also a few customs. I'm going to change a the training area experience rates, and create new training areas, going to put in rock tail,and possibly put in the con skill.
I need a coder to help me code, also a person skilled in making a forums. and someone to help me portforward and also a client coder.
Features that we already have: Dragon claws: only does 2 hits with spec Dagon hai all god swords cape movement with god sword Much more.
Coders: Me another space is open Forum designer: NONE Client coder: NONE Port forward help: NONE (person who helps will get admin or co on my server need to port bad.)
Add my msn if you have questions or would like to apply to me on there MSN: basherf1@live.com
